data.description: Beautiful waterfront home in the desirable Waterleaf community with a great clubhouse, pool and park. Home features 4 bedroom, 3 bath open floor plan with laminate wood flooring throughout main living areas. The Master Bedroom is upgraded with a large walk-in closet. Master bath features separate tub and shower. The large eat-in kitchen opens up nicely to the family room with volume ceilings. Kitchen has  large island with breakfast bar, walnut cabinets, and stainless steel appliances. Enjoy your evenings relaxing in your large backyard overlooking the water in your private fully fenced yard with premium white vinyl fencing. Located on a quiet cul de sac, perfect for gatherings.
